headlines.description: — Tennessee coach Rick Barnes asked the young guys on his bench at halftime, when the fifth-ranked Volunteers were losing to struggling Missouri, what they needed to turn things around over the final 20 minutes.
headlines.shortLinkText: Knecht gets hot in second half, scores 17 as No. 5 Tennessee rallies past Mizzou, 72-67
